Column of Section.

In most cases, one section per page. But in case multi-columns page, sections are used
to distinguish these different layouts.

:::{note}
Currently, support at most two columns.
:::

```
{
    'bbox': (x0, y0, x1, y1),
    'blocks': [{
        ... # block instances
    }, ...],
    'shapes': [{
        ... # shape instances
    }, ...]
}
```

Section of Page.

In most cases, one section per page. But in case multi-columns page, sections are used
to distinguish these different layouts.

:::{note}
Currently, support at most two columns.
:::

```
{
    'bbox': (x0,y0,x1,y1)
    'num_cols': 1,
    'space': 0,
    'columns': [{
        ... # column properties
    }, ...]
}
```
